snippet.title: Home Computer Heroes Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Recorded directly off the Evercade VS.

Games:
00:21 - Attack of the PETSCII Robots (Amiga)
06:00 - Bridge Strike (Amiga)
11:24 - Citadel 'Remonstered' (Amiga)
19:48 - Farming Simulator: C64 Edition (C64)
36:23 - Planet X2 (C64)
42:34 - Tanks Furry (Amiga)
48:52 - The Sword of Ianna (MSX2)

Attack of the PETSCII Robots, Planet X2 (C) David Murray (AKA "The 8-Bit Guy")
Bridge Strike, Tanks Furry (C) Project R3D
Citadel, Citadel 'Remonstered' (C) Virtual Design
Farming Simulator series (C) GIANTS Software
The Sword of Ianna (C) RetroWorks

#retrogames #retrogaming #evercade #evercadeexp #evercadevs #homecomputerheroes #indiegames #homebrew #amiga #c64 #commodore64 #msx2 #attackofthepetsciirobots #planetx2 #the8bitguy #8bitguy #davidmurray #bridgestrike #tanksfurry #projectr3d #citadel #citadelremonstered #virtualdesign #giantssoftware #farmingsimulator #farmingsimulatorc64edition #farmingsimulatorc64 #swordofianna #theswordofianna #retroworks

FUN FACT:
Beside the cart and manual, the box also includes a prologue comic for The Sword of Ianna, as well as a Steam code for Farming Simulator 17.
